We’re all about this toner tip from @samanthasbeautyconfessions! 🙌

“I find that shampooing and conditioning the hair before glossing saves me so much time because I’m not having to spend a ton of time trying to detangle the hair,” she shares. 🚿

Do you shampoo and condition before glossing? Or, is this a new tip for you? Let us know in the comments! 👇
